originalText.text: Great experience coming here for an issue that I had with one of my older tooth fillings. All of the staff were friendly and professional, keeping me informed of potential out of pocket costs and being able to find an appointment for me on short notice. The dentist also did a great job figuring out the issue and fixing it on the same day. Would highly recommend this dental office to anyone nearby!

originalText.text: Highly recommend Emagen Dental! Very clean, modern, with professional staff. They will explain in careful detail about all your options. Very convenient location downtown. Really happy and comforting to have a top notch dental facility for my family and I.

originalText.text: My experience has been wonderful here. Emagen has caring and attentive professionals; beautiful and calming space. Thank you Iryna for taking care of my smile well. Highly recommend this practice.

originalText.text: Can't recommend Emagen Dental highly enough - truly great all-around.  The team is incredibly organized, responsive, and flexible.  Scheduling is always easy and you never have to wait more than a minute or two past your appointment time.  Dr. Urtula is the most engaged dentist I've ever had - always takes time to thoroughly explain what he's doing and why.  Highly recommend.

originalText.text: Been seeing Dr. Urtula for years, and the care from his team is always kind, patient and thorough. Never any unnecessary up-sells. My teeth have been in great shape ever since seeing him.
